title: Full Show (Chiefs beat Raiders on MNF, is Travis Kelce best TE in NFL history, should Mike McCarthy win Coach of the Year?)
description:
00:00 Chiefs beat Raiders 30-29
22:12 Controversial roughing the passer penalty in Chiefs win over Raiders
55:56 Panthers fire Matt Rhule
1:11:58 Has Travis Kelce proven that he is the best tight end in NFL history?
1:23:50 Should Mike McCarthy be coach of the year going undefeated with Cooper Rush at QB?
1:32:07 Davante Adams apologizes for pushing credentialed person as he left the field
1:41:28 Jeanie Buss: "It was my decision to push the button" on the AD trade
1:48:49 Kyrie Irving: Nets are lacking physicality and toughness
1:54:46 Tom Brady jokes about controversial penalty at end of win over Falcons
